---
title: Roasted Veggie Bengali Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: This delightful curry will knock your socks off with its easiness and tastiness. The Indian-inspired Bengal curry paste is a mild yet flavourful base of ginger, chilli, turmeric and fenugreek seeds, and it works perfectly with the roasted parsnip, carrot and courgette to make a mouth-watering meal that's packed with veggie goodness.

